=Open Object Rexx Wiki - Editing a wiki Page=

The following are examples of how to code things in a wiki page. The ooRexx
Wiki uses the MediaWiki formating codes (same as
[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Main_Page WikiPedia]).


----

Paragraphs are seperated by an empty line

Like this. Another paragraph.
More text in the same paragraph.

 Paragraphs are separated by a blank line.

 Like this. Another paragraph.
 More text in the same paragraph.

----
The horizontal lines in this page are made with 4 or more dashes:
 ---- Horizonal line
----

=Top Level Heading=
  =Top Level Heading= (H1)
==Second Level Heading==
  ==Second Level Heading== (H2)
More levels
  === (H3), ==== (H4) etc

----

''italic text'' '''bold text'''

 ''italic text'' '''bold text'''

'''''bold italic text'''''

 '''''bold italic text'''''

----

* level 1
** level 2
**# level 3
**# level 3
**#; level 4 term : level 4 def
**#; level 4 term
**#: level 4 def
* level 1

 * level 1
 ** level 2
 **# level 3
 **# level 3
 **#; level 4 term : level 4 def
 **#; level 4 term
 **#: level 4 def
 * level 1

----

{| border="1"
|+ My caption
!Header 1!!Header 2
!Header 3
|-
| style="background:red; color:white" | Cell 1
|Cell 2|| style="background:black; color:yellow" | Cell 3
|-
|Cell 1 || Cell 2 || Cell 3
|}

 {| border="1"
 |+ My caption
 !Header 1!!Header 2
 !Header 3
 |-
 | style="background:red; color:white" | Cell 1
 |Cell 2|| style="background:black; color:yellow" | Cell 3
 |-
 |Cell 1 || Cell 2 || Cell 3
 |}

